			</span>
		</span></div>
		<div><p>From <em>Javalobby</em>, <a href="http://www.javalobby.org/java/forums/t78187.html">Post Modern Programming</a>:</p>


	<blockquote>
		<p>Indeed, I specifically site [<em>sic</em>] where <span class="caps">OOP</span> explicitly fails and even should be regarded as an anti-pattern.</p>
	</blockquote>


	<p>Indeed, why anyone would care what  Roger Voss regards as &#8220;anti-pattern&#8221; is a mystery to me, but I will note that I <a href="/n8/articles/2006/08/08/scripting-a-very-good-sheet-with-a-hole-in-it">saw this coming</a>.</p></div>
